00:34:10,381 --> 00:34:11,632
É o Luther.

484
00:34:11,716 --> 00:34:12,759
Está me ouvindo?

485
00:34:13,426 --> 00:34:14,552
Michael, escute.

486
00:34:15,178 --> 00:34:16,763
Vão matá-lo.

487
00:34:18,389 --> 00:34:19,223
Mike.

